    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2239422966" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer840055974482125224">I enjoy books about India. This fictional tale included a lot about the history of India at the end of the 19th century and on into the 20th century. It is told through the life of a Princess whose parents marry her off to the son of a Maharaja. In the narrative, we learn a lot about life in Royal India and about the British attitude to India and Indians.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


